plptool.gui

Class ProjectEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • plptool.gui.ProjectEvent

  • public class ProjectEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    Project event. Some actions in PLPTool will pass an instance of this class to the hook function of all loaded dynamic modules.
